title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Be generous, especially if thats what your heart compels you to do now. On the other hand, if you give to get, youre likely to be disappointed with a partner or dear one. The touchy Moon in your sign allows you to shine and burst into peoples lives with kindness and perceptiveness. Of course, not everyone can receive all that you have to offer, so dispense your wisdom and affection in appropriate doses. However, theres no need to overcompensate and miss the chance to connect emotionally. Author Paulo Coelho wrote, Anyone who loves in the expectation of being loved in return is wasting their time.
